links.title: PayPal to offer crypto payments starting in 2021
links.description: PayPal announced on Wednesday its entry into the cryptocurrency market, according to multiple reports. PayPal customers will be able to use cryptocurrencies to shop at any merchant in its large network starting from early 2021, the company said. The payments will be settled through fiat currencies, similar to many existing crypto merchant solutions like BitPay.
